==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nidamental
<hw>Nid`a*men"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>nidamentum</ets> materials for a nest, fr. <ets>nidus</ets> nest.
See <er>Nest</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to, or
bearing, eggs or egg capsules; <as>as, the <ex>nidamental</ex> capsules
of certain gastropods; <ex>nidamental</ex> glands</as>. See
<ex>Illust</ex>. of <er>Dibranchiata</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nidary</ent>⟦br⟧
